The '''Canyonade''' was a location on [[Cejansij]]. It was a large canyon that had been turned into a city, similar to those on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]]. It contained the [[Grand Rim Promenade]], [[Docking Rectangle 16]], and [[Tranquility Common]].

